name: Welcome to Jersey
summary: As summer begins on the Channel island of Jersey, seven of the most glamourous residents prepare themselves for luxury estate agent Margaret Thompson's annual party. Fun-loving Kate intends to grab everyone's attention by arriving in style; daredevil Hedi enlists best friends Jono and Cisco to accompany her to the party; while new mum Ashley braces herself for a return to the social scene; and former model Mia considers a new career.

name: Forgive-Me-Nots
summary:
Whilst Kate celebrates her birthday, a text from a special someone brings a smile to her face even if confusion surrounds her long-awaited introduction to Tessa. Could first impressions be the wrong impressions or is Tessa ready to give Kate a second chance?

Mia's hopes for a return to modelling are boosted when Hedi offers some unexpected advice whilst Ashley reaches out to Margaret and discovers a sympathetic friend.

Meanwhile Jersey's social butterflies flutter towards the local lido for a night of fun and frolics but some ladies reveal a touch too much… don't they Jane?

name: Two Strikes and You're In
summary: Mia gets the opportunity of a lifetime when she throws an extravagant dinner party.

name: I Should Coco
summary: Margaret hosts Coco Chanel Thompson's fourth birthday party, and the long-awaited meet-up between Kate and Tessa leaves their relationship in a sticky situation.

name: Highcliffe, High Class
summary: Tessa has high hopes for the housewives' staycation, but will everyone behave themselves?

name: A Grave Concern
summary: With the Staycation in full flow, the Housewives bond over a game of Truth or Dare, and Margaret's pulse is left racing by a surprise guest.

name: Ladies Who Launch
summary: Mia questions her relationships with some of the women following the disastrous dinner party, while Kate and Margaret regret not being more outspoken.

name: Fake Orgasm Addicts
summary: Kate's ambition of starting a charity gets off to a rocky start, while Mia's dreams of returning to modelling become a reality. Plus, Tessa celebrates her birthday.

name: A Splash for Ash
summary: The fallout from Tessa and Mia's latest argument leads to a summit to clear the air, whil Ashley's relationship with Jane takes an unexpected twist.

name: La Finn
summary: As summer comes to the sun-soaked island of Jersey, the Hartmanns celebrate with...a chalet ski party! Kate focuses her attention on building bridges with Finn.
